Phase D.2.a -- KNY 2017 º8.5.17 differential Lax pull
========================================================================

KNY 2017 eq. 8.237 (Hamiltonian H_{D_6}^{KNY}):
  H = (1/t) * [p(p-1) q^2 + (a_1 + a_2) q p + t p - a_2 q]
     with a_0 + a_1 = 1.

KNY 2017 eq. 8.239 (Lax operator L_1):
  L_1 = rho_0(x; q, p, t, a_1, a_2)
      + rho_1(x; q, a_1, a_2, t) * d/dx
      + d^2/dx^2
  rho_0 = -a_2/x + p q / (x (x-q)) - t H / x^2
  rho_1 = (1 + a_1 + a_2)/x - 1/(x-q) + t/x^2 - 1

V_quad parameter point (CT v1.3 º3.5):
  (alpha_inf, alpha_0, beta_inf, beta_0) = (1/6, 0, 0, -1/2)
  Okamoto null-sum: alpha_inf+alpha_0+beta_inf+beta_0 = -1/3
  ANOMALY D2: null-sum != 0; sums to -1/3.

